snippet.textDisplay: My favorite 1st person puzzler of all time right there, in good company with Antichamber and the Portal series. The soundtrack played a big part in creating its amazing atmosphere, with each level having its own theme. This reminds me that I need to try The Talos Principle, but it will be a while until Fallout 4 gets its claws off me.

snippet.textDisplay:
+SupraDarky Qbeh-1 is so good, so relaxing to play, and its OST is wonderful. 
If you like 1st Person puzzler, you need to do The Talos Principle and its DLC Road To Gehenna, they are at least as good (if not better) as Portal 2.
